These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, action
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, artichoke
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Food   | cucumber | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, subway
1. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Transport   | subway | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, game
1. the game-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |
| Cigar   | game | bolivar |

 #################################

 
